RACE.FOOTNOTES: DRIVEN BY SPEED was reserved early on the inside, advanced up the inside on the far turn, angled out leaving the three sixteenths to the far outside and closed well to edge away late to prove best under a drive. FILLMORE EAST was three wide into the first turn, then settled two wide, and was between rivals by the half mile marker, then advanced three wide on the turn, then was fanned out five wide leaving the turn while making a bid, then continued well but was outfinished by the winner while getting the nod for the place award. COMPLETE was rated along the inside, advanced on the turn on the inside, then swung out four wide and forcing FILLMORE EAST out leaving the turn, made a bid but was out-kicked while losing the bob for the place award. SERENE WARRIOR tracked the pace two wide, made a two wide bid on the turn to duel for command, then weakened the final furlong. FROSTED WILD RIDE was keen early to set the early pace while clear, then was headed on the turn and dueled for the lead to the three sixteenths and then weakened the final furlong. BLIND SIGHT was three wide into the first turn, then settled three wide on the backstretch and tired. YOURINDENIAL failed to menace.
